barkText.en: Good work, everyone.
We made another step forward, Endfielders.

barkText.cn: 别担心，武库工程师会帮忙保养的。
barkText.en: Don't worry. The arsenal engineers will get them repaired.
Shiny stuff. Let's get some more.
New knowledge gained.
Mission complete. It was a walk on a cake.

barkText.cn: 通往终末地目标的路上，又少了一些障碍。
barkText.en: Alrighty, another hurdle down! Onward to our goal!

barkText.cn: 耶！刚刚的配合简直完美！
barkText.en: Yay! That was some perfect teamwork!
That move of yours was incredible!

barkText.cn: 要不要来一片奶酪？有助于体力恢复喔！
barkText.en: Want some cheese? It's great for restoring your stamina!
Nominal conditions restored.

barkText.cn: 速战速决，我们还有事要办。
barkText.en: Make this quick. We got other things to do.

barkText.cn: 我人生中的大部分经历都在教我一件事：学会接受每一次失败，然后想办法跨过去。
barkText.en: Most of my experiences in life taught me one thing: Accept your defeats, and find a way to surmount them.

barkText.cn: 是正面作战任务，执行方案A！
barkText.en: We're going head-to-head, execute Plan A!

barkText.cn: 到了不得不战斗的时候了吗？上吧。
barkText.en: Do we really have to fight? Fine. Let's go.
That's right, hold on to that spirit!
Initiating emergency treatment.

barkText.cn: 怎么样？消除得干干净净！
barkText.en: Absolute neutralization! What do you think?
The bounties of the land.
Well done.
That deserves a medal.
Incredible.

barkText.cn: 秘笈总是放在这种箱子里面呢！
barkText.en: They usually hide secret tomes in crates like this.
"So wowed and amazed"...??
Alright, Chen. That's enough flattery for the day...
Awesome!
Beautiful!
Wonder when I'll get that good.

barkText.cn: 只有徒步行走在这片大地上，我们才能感受到生命的气息……这也是终末地战斗的意义。
barkText.en: Only by walking upon the land, can we truly appreciate every breath and pulse of life... And this is what Endfield is fighting for.
Now it's time to bring the pain.

barkText.cn: 团队合作总是更高效点……一起挖吧。
barkText.en: We are always more efficient working as a team... Let's mine this together.

barkText.cn: 收集矿物吗？我也来帮忙。
barkText.en: Collecting minerals? Allow me to assist.
Let me take point!

barkText.cn: 报告未知区域，有进一步行动指示吗？
barkText.en: Unidentified area detected. Awaiting additional instructions for action.
I'd rather not do this too often...
Yeah... Everyone played a part.

barkText.cn: 我探查到了珍奇的存在。
barkText.en: I have perceived the existence of rarities.

barkText.cn: 我来帮忙了……不过……别对我有太多期望……
barkText.en: I'm here to help... But don't expect too much from me...

barkText.cn: 发现不少有用资源，等下可以筛选一些用作设备维护的材料。
barkText.en: Rich resource stash found. We should sort through it to identify gear maintenance materials.
All equipment charged and ready.
A remarkable discovery.
A much-needed set of intel.

barkText.cn: 前面的敌人很危险！各位小心！
barkText.en: Everyone! Be cautious! That enemy looks very dangerous!
Had my fill of food and sleep. Let's keep going.

barkText.cn: 人们是怎么看待塔卫二的？
barkText.en: So, what do people think about Talos-II?
Heh! Just doing my job!
Unity delivers blade synergy!
Hmph. I'm better now.
Nice!
Not bad!
Ha! You deserve a high five!

barkText.cn: 我的小暴鸰有点紧张，那家伙应该很厉害！
barkText.en: Tweety-Bomb looks a little nervous. That one's probably a naughty big bad.

barkText.cn: 终于有机会休整一下了。佩丽卡，你饿不饿？
barkText.en: Finally a chance to stretch my legs. Perlica, you hungry?

barkText.cn: 群策群力之下，再没有难事。
barkText.en: When we pool our strength, no task is beyond us.

barkText.cn: 对！我就是这个意思。嗯……思维方式灵活变通，眼界也十分开阔。
barkText.en: Yeah! That's totally what I meant. Your mind is lightning quick, and you got some great plans and vision.

barkText.cn: 从接到任务那一刻起，我就在好奇管理员会是个什么样的人，实际见到后，感觉真是不可思议。
barkText.en: I was so curious about the Endmin when I first received this mission. Then when I saw the actual Endmin, I was like, you know, so wowed and amazed.

barkText.cn: 那些地方适合隐匿行踪，是潜入或跟踪时的最佳选择，需要特别提防。
barkText.en: Perfect hiding spots. Prime choices for trackers and infiltrators. Gotta keep your eyes peeled for them.
Feeling better?

barkText.cn: 刚才我做得不够好……请各位放心，我会吸取经验，加以改进。
barkText.en: I didn't perform well... But I'll take what I've learned and sharpen up. I promise.
Best thing I've done today!

barkText.cn: 嘿嘿，刚才的表现还不错吧？
barkText.en: Heheh. I pulled it off, right?

barkText.cn: 我一直想要一款像这样流光变幻的指甲油。
barkText.en: Such fluid, effervescent glittering. I've always wanted my nails varnished like that.
Not bad. Everyone did their part.
And I was hoping you'd say that.

barkText.cn: 再检查一遍背包吧……以免有什么遗漏。
barkText.en: I should check my backpack again ... see if I missed anything.
Watch it. Don't push yourself.
I ... I feel better...
Don't panic! I got you covered!

barkText.cn: 没想到吧？我有专门对付石头的剑法。
barkText.en: Didn't expect this, right? My special swordmancy for rocky stuff!

barkText.cn: 这些物资最好都收集起来，救援时说不定能用上！
barkText.en: We should gather these resources! They might come in handy for rescue operations.

barkText.cn: 不要心急，调整完毕后再做打算。
barkText.en: No need to worry. We'll regroup and sort this out.
My blade is still intact.

barkText.cn: 信使准则：未知区域需要谨慎前行！
barkText.en: According to messenger standards: Be extra cautious when entering uncharted territories!
We're in perfect sync.
You pulled off a sleek move.

barkText.cn: 不知道这次行动会怎么安排……嗯，还是根据已有情报，多拟几份应急预案吧！
barkText.en: I wonder how we'd go about this operation... Hmm. I better refer to the intel we have and come up with a few emergency backup plans!
A well-deserved victory.

barkText.cn: 不畏强敌，不损己命……出色的战斗。
barkText.en: We fought with both courage and prudence. Excellent work, everyone.

barkText.cn: 这次的报酬，留到复仇时再结吧。
barkText.en: Let's save this payment for when we take our revenge.

barkText.cn: 既有的一切，先于我们便在大地上了——我们要用双手去取得。
barkText.en: All have been set upon this Land before us — And with the toil of our hands shall they be acquired.
Something important lies over there!
Yep, yep. We totally couldn't have done it without you.
Let me help as well!

barkText.cn: 那或许是你们需要的东西。
barkText.en: You might find that useful.

barkText.cn: 那儿是不是有什么东西？
barkText.en: Hm, I think I spot some goodies over there?

barkText.cn: 根据经验，那边应该有可以收集的东西。
barkText.en: Experience tells me that there are gatherables over there.

barkText.cn: 这种稀罕物挺不错，安排一下收集工作吧。
barkText.en: A very rare finding. Time to assign gathering work.

barkText.cn: 无论如何，至少达成了这次的任务目标。
barkText.en: In any case, we still completed the mission objectives.
Sorry...! Let me catch my breath!

barkText.cn: 不利的因素最好从一开始就解决掉。
barkText.en: Adverse variables are best taken out during the earliest phases of war.
All variables within estimates.

barkText.cn: 来帮忙啦！爆破什么的我很擅长哦！
barkText.en: Here to help! I happen to be an expert demolitionist!

barkText.cn: 先确认伤员的状态，采用安全队形，重整旗鼓。
barkText.en: Check all injuries. Assume defensive formation and restore combat readiness.
I remember that you kinda like these.

barkText.cn: 捡到这么好的东西，是不是要上交给巡卫啊……
barkText.en: Nice find. Do we really have to turn it over to the watchguards...?

barkText.cn: 保险起见，最好慎重行动。
barkText.en: We should play it safe and approach with care.

barkText.cn: 那个家伙，似乎回绝了谈判的可能哦。
barkText.en: Looks like that guy's shut down any chance of negotiations.
Thank you all!
Thanks for the thumbs up!
Everyone is rested.

barkText.cn: 优质的矿藏……它们将成为我手中的利剑与坚盾。
barkText.en: This'll shape up nicely — perfect for both offense and defense.

barkText.cn: 祖宗们在雷姆必拓时的老手艺！
barkText.en: Witness the skills passed down by my Rim Billiton ancestors!
I'll distract them.

barkText.cn: 哎呀，被听到了？独自旅行就是会养成自言自语的习惯……很好听？那就再奖励你一段！
barkText.en: *Humming* Oops, you caught that? It's a habit I got from traveling solo... Did you like it? I'll sing another one just for you!
WARHH, dodge the attack!
A very professional move!
We make a good team!

barkText.cn: 嗯，我们都为终末地尽了一份力！
barkText.en: Great job. We've all done our part for Endfield!

barkText.cn: 这些矿物是对终末地有用的物资。
barkText.en: These minerals are essential materials for Endfield.
Time to fight.
Conditions stabilized.
This feels familiar.

barkText.cn: 这就是醚质吧？好漂亮！赶紧收好吧！
barkText.en: Is this Aurylene? How pretty... We should stash it properly!
Engage.

barkText.cn: 人不是机器，需要时间休整。
barkText.en: People are not machines, and must set aside time for rest.

barkText.cn: ……与其苦着一张脸，不如先动起来。这事还没完呢。
barkText.en: Moping won't get us anywhere, but action will. C'mon, this isn't over yet.

barkText.cn: 我没把脏东西溅出去吧？
barkText.en: I hope I didn't spill that dirty goop all over the place.

barkText.cn: 无需因失败感到耻辱，正视它，然后让它成为你更进一步的垫脚石。
barkText.en: Don't let failure weigh you down. Own it, and let it propel you to greater heights.
Everyone, we've got a new buddy to play with.

barkText.cn: 获得醚质的战略意义恐怕高于它本身的价值。
barkText.en: Its strategic significance probably exceeds its operational value.

barkText.cn: 醚质，如果终末地认为它有价值的话……
barkText.en: Aurylene... I guess Endfield finds it valuable.

barkText.cn: “物超所值，巫术时刻！”……不对。“巫术时刻——”……还是不对……
barkText.en: "True value found nowhere else. Witching Hour!" ...That doesn't sound right. "Witching Hoooourrr—" ...Hnngh. That's not right either...
Look, over there...

barkText.cn: 唔……所谓其意自见……我究竟漏了什么呢……
barkText.en: Hmm... People say that the essence shall reveal itself... Is there something I missed...?
You've got this, and you've got me!

barkText.cn: 那是他们最脆弱的时候……我们不能让这些裂地者为所欲为。
barkText.en: They prey on people at their most vulnerable. We can't let these raiders get away with it.

barkText.cn: 看看那边，说不定会有惊喜！
barkText.en: Look there! Maybe there's a surprise waiting for us!

barkText.cn: 难怪开拓区外围的定居点时常传来遭裂地者袭扰的报告，却又总是追踪不到他们……
barkText.en: That explains why the settlements on the frontier outskirts kept reporting Landbreaker attacks, but we were never able to track them down…

barkText.cn: 找到一点好东西，我能全拿走吗？
barkText.en: Found something cool, mind if I take it all?
Yeah! We can now continue our journey.

barkText.cn: 这个……挺神奇的，我能再看看吗？
barkText.en: Looks like ... magical stuff. Can I take another look?
Feeling better.
These minerals may come in handy.

barkText.cn: 要想在开拓区活下来，关键在于如何避开危险，找到一条安全的路径。
barkText.en: Survival in the frontiers is all about finding a safe route.

barkText.cn: 但裂地者往往会埋伏在这些地方，专门袭击那些自以为脱险的人。
barkText.en: But Landbreakers often ambush where you'd expect it least, waiting to pounce the moment you drop your guard.

barkText.cn: 我也来帮忙，我们是搭档嘛！
barkText.en: Let me give you a hand! We're a team, right?
Impressive maneuver.

barkText.cn: 配合得不错，回去给各位加餐。
barkText.en: Such teamwork deserves a feast.
Don't worry, I'm okay.

barkText.cn: 那附近我也没去过。走，咱们去瞧瞧！
barkText.en: Never been to that place. Let's head over for a closer look.
Get to somewhere safe!

barkText.cn: 想在这里获得更多情报，看来得费点工夫了。
barkText.en: Looks like we don't get to squeeze any more intel out of them.

barkText.cn: 醚质是破碎的宇宙，它穿越了遥远的距离才抵达我们面前。
barkText.en: Aurylene is a fragment of a shattered universe. This one traveled massive distances to be here, right before us.

barkText.cn: 这种品质的树木可不多。
barkText.en: Wood of this quality is rare.

barkText.cn: 与侵蚀和裂隙不同，醚质没有那么危险呢。
barkText.en: Unlike the Blight and rifts, Aurylenes aren't that dangerous.

barkText.cn: 前方似乎存在许多不确定因素，让我去调查吧！
barkText.en: Something feels unclear up ahead. Leave the scouting to me!

barkText.cn: 这里让我想起了荒野里的篝火，而且似乎有同样的温度。
barkText.en: This reminds me of campfires in the wildlands. Both seem to share the same warmth.
It is worth a celebration.

barkText.cn: 没关系……比起我们的目标……
barkText.en: I'm good... Focus on our objective...
One sec, just need a quick breather!

barkText.cn: 真知的赐予就在附近，去将它取得。
barkText.en: If a gift of Veritas is nearby, then it shall be retrieved.

barkText.cn: 经验再丰富的牙兽群，捕猎也不会每次都成功。但至少，我们学到了教训。
barkText.en: Even the most experienced tuskbeast pack can fail to bring down their prey. At least we learned something from this hunt.
Just as I predicted.
Wasn't expecting anything less.

barkText.cn: 歇歇，磨刀不误砍柴工嘛！
barkText.en: Good rest! Sharpened blades make up for lost time!

barkText.cn: 我不饿……你好好歇会儿吧，为接下来的行动养足精神。
barkText.en: I'm alright... Get some quality rest, Chen. We're still counting on your positive spirit.
Where should we go next?
See? I knew this would come in handy.

barkText.cn: 这就是塞什卡的尖端技术！啊，习惯改不掉了……
barkText.en: Made possible by Seš'qa's latest technology! Ah... I can't break this habit...
I hope I didn't break my combat outfit...

barkText.cn: 工作手册上写过，适当休息有助于更好地完成任务。
barkText.en: Adequate rest is conducive to mission completion. That's what the work manual says.
Wow! You're awesome.
Nice! You're a true pro!
Alrighty!

barkText.cn: 危险的气息，是个棘手的敌人。
barkText.en: I sense danger. This one won't go down easily.

barkText.cn: 未知的区域，切记保持队形。
barkText.en: Maintain formation, especially in uncharted territories.
Let's go check it out!
Got it! I'll take a look!
If it helps with survival, bring it.

barkText.cn: 这些东西可以拿去卖吗？
barkText.en: Can we actually sell this?

barkText.cn: 还有这种好东西？幸好上面没写名字。
barkText.en: Wooo, what a find. And no name tag? Hmm...
Time to fight.
Nicely done!
Let me help you.

barkText.cn: 无论身处何种境地，时刻保持警惕都是我最基本的原则。
barkText.en: Constant vigilance in every place and situation. This is a rule that I never break.
Be careful!

barkText.cn: 一些重要的新发现，不去看看吗？
barkText.en: We should take a look at that key discovery.

barkText.cn: 终于能歇一歇了，发型都乱了，得赶紧整理下。
barkText.en: Whew. Been waiting for this break forever. Gotta tame this wild hair...

barkText.cn: 战斗已经结束了，没必要为失败纠结，下次遇到的话注意点不就好了？
barkText.en: Don't sweat the loss. Let's just be more careful next time. We've got this, yeah?

barkText.cn: 我们有照顾彼此的传统哦！
barkText.en: We Rim Billies always take care of one another!
Ahhh... I'm feeling much better!

barkText.cn: 前方异常反应，不像是锚点活动……要去看看吗？
barkText.en: Unusual signals detected ahead. Not matching known Ankhor patterns. Shall we investigate?
You've done well.
I find no issue with that.
This is deserving of praise.
Good thing I packed this one.

barkText.cn: 我会为我们所有人祈祷。
barkText.en: I shall offer prayers for all of us.
I am fortunate to be in your company.

barkText.cn: 我以前也有过一个。嗯……后来的事不太让人高兴呢。
barkText.en: I had one of these before... What happened after wasn't so great.

barkText.cn: 呼……幸好在体力槽见底前结束了。
barkText.en: Hoo... So glad I didn't pass out halfway through.

barkText.cn: 总算结束了……哈，我表现得还不错吧……
barkText.en: Huh... It's over... I did well, right...?
Understood. I'm covering your flank.

barkText.cn: 希望它们有足够的价值，配得上我们费的功夫。
barkText.en: I hope their worth can pay for our efforts.
I'm giving you a LIKE!
Not bad at all!
You're really good at this!
Incredible!
Great!
Awesome!

barkText.cn: 比预想的麻烦不少……但，胜者是我们，这就够了。
barkText.en: It was harder than I thought... But we are the victors. That's what counts.
Incoming! Watch out!

barkText.cn: 来一趟不容易，能带多少带多少。
barkText.en: Finding this is not easy. Fill your pockets with whatever you can.

barkText.cn: 现在可以坐下来，思考行动、修缮装备、检查背包，并且享用热咖啡。
barkText.en: Phew, now I can finally sit down and enjoy my coffee. Oh, I should also plan the next steps, fix up my gear, and check my bag.

barkText.cn: 警惕比火焰更危险的存在。
barkText.en: Be cautious. This is far more dangerous than fire.
W-we all did a good job!

barkText.cn: 我特别好奇全盛时期的管理员是怎么战斗的，佩丽卡你见过吗？
barkText.en: I'm really curious how the Endmin fought at full power. Perlica, have you seen that before?

barkText.cn: 管理员的作战风格真让人印象深刻。
barkText.en: So, the Endmin's fighting style is pretty unique and impressive.

barkText.cn: 人们从夹缝中苦苦争取来了如今的局面……毫无疑问，我们都无比珍惜这个新的家园。
barkText.en: Humanity fought hard for every inch to get to where we are today. There's no doubt we truly cherish this new home.

barkText.cn: 回顾文明环带的变迁……我们已经在危机四伏的塔卫二创造了一段漫长的历史。
barkText.en: Looking back, the Civilization Band has come a long way... We've carved out a long history in this perilous world.

barkText.cn: 从我们抵达塔卫二起，这颗星球就既包容又排斥着我们。
barkText.en: Since we first set foot on Talos-II, it has both embraced us and resisted us.
Awesome teamwork!
Fabulous work!

barkText.cn: 换我来吧，体力活，我的强项。
barkText.en: Let me do it. I'm good with physical work.
I'll distract them.
War is never about mercy.

barkText.cn: 那东西好稀罕！我们上那边看看去？
barkText.en: Rare stuff spotted. Shall we check it out?

barkText.cn: 呼，打完了，抓紧时间休整下吧。
barkText.en: Hoo. The battle has ended. Let's take a break while we still can.

barkText.cn: 大家都在努力，我也要变得更强才行！
barkText.en: Everyone's giving their all. I've got to step up too!

barkText.cn: 发现高价值目标，申请开展收集行动。
barkText.en: High-value object identified. Requesting approval to initiate collection operation.
Watch out... Don't get hit.
High-threat hostile. Approach with caution.

barkText.cn: 得来不易的好东西，想清楚了再用吧。
barkText.en: Took a lot to get this. Let's put it to good use.
Let's show 'em what we got!

barkText.cn: 附近有需要调查的区域。
barkText.en: The nearby area needs a proper survey.
Hrraak... I'm not doing too well.

barkText.cn: 是醚质！你怎么知道我喜欢发着亮光的东西？
barkText.en: Aurylene?! How did you know I love stuff that shines?
Take cover, NOW!

barkText.cn: 您这话在理，赢得确实爽！
barkText.en: Well said! It was fun, and we won!

barkText.cn: 呃……我感觉自己的身上正在承受整个世界的重担……主要是膝盖……
barkText.en: Hngh... Feels like the weight of the entire world has come down at me ... my knees, especially...
Keep up. We need a closer look.
Clearing the way for the rescue!

barkText.cn: 好像全身涌过一股暖流……我得起来热热身，活动活动！
barkText.en: I feel a warm surge coursing through me... Time to get up and stretch a little!
An easy victory.
Hooo— I wouldn't expect anything less.

barkText.cn: 荒野中的每一件事物，都在磨砺中成长。
barkText.en: Every wildland being must endure hardship to grow.

barkText.cn: 好像有一些值得注意的东西，去查看一下吧？
barkText.en: I think I spotted something interesting over there... Let's go check it out!

barkText.cn: 您放开手干，其他我替您包圆咯！
barkText.en: Call the shots! I'll do the rest!
Nicely done.
You did well. Much appreciated.
Lovely find. Well done!

barkText.cn: 一些醚质在我们接近时会突然闪避，这是为什么？某种能量互斥？
barkText.en: Some Aurylenes suddenly move away when we approach. Why? Can it be some form of energy-based repulsion?

barkText.cn: 发现高威胁目标，保持警戒。
barkText.en: High-threat hostile detected. Stay alert.
Keep going ... gotta keep going...

barkText.cn: 待会儿可以把矿物鉴定分选一下。
barkText.en: I'll sort and identify these minerals in a bit.

barkText.cn: 我突然想到一个笑话，有人想听吗？……哎，给点反应嘛。
barkText.en: Yo, I just thought of a joke. Anyone wanna hear it? Hey, a little reaction, please.
Feeling better?
It's what I'm expected to do.
Just being part of the team.

barkText.cn: 嗯……我这算是重操旧业了？
barkText.en: Back to my old gig, huh?

barkText.cn: 发现可用物资，准备回收。
barkText.en: Useful resources located. Prepare for salvage.

barkText.cn: 正直头颈，松肩沉肘，含胸拔背，松腰落胯，沉稳腿脚，起——哎呀哎呀，我在忙！
barkText.en: Neck straight, shoulders relaxed, chest in, hips loose, legs firm. Here goes — shoo, shoo! I'm busy!
Spectacular!
You're so amazing, team!

barkText.cn: 三人行必有我师，我们有四个人！
barkText.en: Two heads are better than one, and four are even better!
Heh heh, you're making me blush...

barkText.cn: 发现宝物！咱们快过去看看！
barkText.en: I spot treasure! Let's go take a look!

barkText.cn: 哇，金色！哈哈，和您逗闷子呢！
barkText.en: The golden jackpot! Hah! Just messing with you!

barkText.cn: 已经做得很好了。下一次先把棘手的交给我。
barkText.en: You did alright. Just leave the hard fighting to me next time.

barkText.cn: 多少恢复了些体力……能再多休息会儿就更好了。
barkText.en: I'm a little recovered ... still, a bit more rest would be great.
Enemy sighted! Let me handle this!
Don't just stand there, move!
A good captain ... should never back down...

barkText.cn: 我见过其他人使用宏山的剑法，但即便是同样的剑招，每个人的章法也不尽相同……
barkText.en: You know, I've seen other Hongshan swordmancers, and everyone seems to perform the same move differently...
Roger. Engaging the enemy.

barkText.cn: 潘叔说，出枪不是比手快，而是看谁心稳，这口气我还是没沉住。歇口气，再来一次。
barkText.en: Uncle Pan says that being a great lancer isn't about speed, it's about keeping your cool. I lost mine this time, but I'll regroup and go again!
Much better now.
Wow, perfect execution!
Beautifully done! I'm amazed!

barkText.cn: 嘘……管理员好像在休息？长途跋涉是一件很累人的事情。轻一点，让管理员多歇一会儿。
barkText.en: Shhh... I think the Endmin's catching some rest. Long distance hauls can get really tiring. Let's keep it down and give the Endmin some quiet time to unwind.
Incredible!
You did the right thing.
I knew you could do it!

barkText.cn: 真正有价值的东西经得住火炼。
barkText.en: Only true valuables survive the flame.

barkText.cn: 嘘，平时看到这种好东西，我们都会先埋起来……
barkText.en: Shhhh! We usually bury these good finds first before anyone else spots them...
Focus on the battle, not me.

barkText.cn: 是无人机还没探测到的地带，大家多注意防范。
barkText.en: Our drones haven't surveyed this area. We should be alert, people.

barkText.cn: 所有人，注意指令——抱歉，刚才有点走神，请不要在意。
barkText.en: All hands, stay alert for orders — Oh ... apologies, I was spacing out. Please pardon my lapse.

barkText.cn: 我不擅长持久战……加速解决吧。
barkText.en: I'm no good in long battles... Please finish it quickly.
I wish you the best of fortune.

barkText.cn: 这条路你认识吗？我们好像还没走过。
barkText.en: You sure you know this path? I don't think we've been down it before.
Your eyes burn with insight.
You follow wisdom without delay.
Let me help out.
Leave it to me.

barkText.cn: 剩下的交给我吧，用剑更快！
barkText.en: Leave the rest to me! It's faster with a blade!

barkText.cn: 看到个好地方。嗯……应该会很有意思。
barkText.en: Found a nice spot. Hmm ... seems like fun.
There. Nice and clean.

barkText.cn: 要是那时候也能消除侵蚀的话……
barkText.en: If only I could've eliminated the Blight back then...
Something important lies over there!

barkText.cn: 不错，出招比之前更快了。
barkText.en: Impressive. You got faster.

barkText.cn: 战场上变数太多，连“小嘀嗒”都无法预测……但下次我们肯定能做得更好！
barkText.en: Battles are hard to predict, even for Tink-a-Bella... *BUT* we'll definitely do better next time.
Woo, looks like you're quicker than me!
Y'know, a curious mind is worth more than any hidden treasure.
This is one rewarding trip.
We're so committed! Fingers crossed for a bonus.

barkText.cn: 太好了，这下不用多绕路了。
barkText.en: Great. Now we don't have to walk the long way round.

barkText.cn: 走了那么多路，大家的脚步都有些沉重，是该好好休息一下了！
barkText.en: We've walked so far ... everyone must be tired. Good call on the break.
Patching up. Stay alert.
Careful now. Don't push it.

barkText.cn: 武、武库那边，不会有意见吧？
barkText.en: The Ar-arsenal people ... won't get mad about this, right?

barkText.cn: 空气很干燥，今晚天气不错，应该能睡个好觉。
barkText.en: The air is dry and the skies look good. I shall rest well tonight.
Stay awake...! I can't fall here...

barkText.cn: 其实有时候，我反倒将这个视为躲开某些人的自保措施呢。
barkText.en: Honestly, I actually see it as a way to keep myself safe from certain people.
Your meds! Catch.
Let me help out.

barkText.cn: 不得了，这可都是稀有资源！真走运。
barkText.en: Wow! A load of super-rares! We struck the jackpot!

barkText.cn: 那就和你们一起欢呼吧。
barkText.en: Guess I'll join your celebrations.
I knew we could do it.

barkText.cn: 弹药清点完毕，下一轮狩猎该开始了。
barkText.en: Ammo check complete. Time for the next hunt.

barkText.cn: 如果还觉得冷，可以往我这边靠。
barkText.en: Try getting closer to me if you're still feeling cold.
Watch your step, people.
It's okay. I can tough it out...

barkText.cn: 别气馁，撑过了这场风雪就离目的地更近了！所以先保存体力，争取早点抵达安全地带！
barkText.en: Don't feel bad. Endure the storm and approach our goal! Save our strength and we'll reach the safe zone early!

barkText.cn: 我又看到了丰饶的景象——是律法应许的福地！
barkText.en: Again I behold abundance — a blessing promised by the Law!
Want a piece of panda? COME AT ME!

barkText.cn: 之前的准备派上用场了……
barkText.en: Guess the prep was worth it.
Hmph. I'll remember that.
Not bad. I'll handle the next one.

barkText.cn: 侵蚀已经无法威胁如今的终末地。
barkText.en: The Blight no longer threatens the Endfield of today.
Thanks for your support!
Let's keep up the good work!
Have I made the same mistakes again...?
Look out! Danger!
Well, that was something.

barkText.cn: 真卖力，边上可没摄像机呀。
barkText.en: Not bad. Shame no one's here to film it.
...Caught my breath again.
An impressive acquisition.
Intel received. Thank you.
A useful reminder. Much appreciated.

barkText.cn: 这种程度还不能让我倒下。
barkText.en: Not enough to take me down.

barkText.cn: 圆又圆，亮晶晶……原来醚质是这个大小啊。
barkText.en: It's round and it's shiny... Oh, this is the actual size of Aurylene.

barkText.cn: 也许是福地，也许是恶土，但凭我们探寻。
barkText.en: Blessed or accursed, the realm is ours to explore.

barkText.cn: 我们坚持到了最后……嗯，艰辛的过程是值得的。
barkText.en: We made it to the end... And the difficulties were worth their while.

barkText.cn: 这也是一种珍贵的物资，尽快收集比较好。
barkText.en: A rare material. We should gather them quickly.
Our teamwork just keeps getting better.
You flatter me.
I don't even feel tired.

barkText.cn: 刚才真危险啊，不过最后还是完美收工。
barkText.en: Things got a little intense, but we nailed it.
We handled that fight well!

barkText.cn: 我不会再让这种情况发生。
barkText.en: I will not allow this to happen again.
Ooh. Bravo!
Heheh. What a happy day!
Wow! This is great!
Quick! Take some of this!

barkText.cn: 我们不会被这些困难阻止。
barkText.en: No hardship will stop us.

barkText.cn: 总算赢了，多利先生累不累？
barkText.en: We've done it. Hope you're not tired, Mr. Dolly.

barkText.cn: 矿物是工业的基础，多准备一些吧。
barkText.en: Mineral ores form the foundation of industry. We should gather more.

barkText.cn: 太慢了，我不喜欢干等着。
barkText.en: Too slow. I hate standing around with nothing to do.
Outstanding technique. Impressive.
We are united as one!

barkText.cn: 您的术式令我耳目一新！
barkText.en: Your Arts have opened my eyes!

barkText.cn: 无需话语，便能传递我们的联结！
barkText.en: We are united beyond the need for words!

barkText.cn: 休整完毕，各位，准备继续行动。
barkText.en: R&R complete. Team, make ready to continue our operations.

barkText.cn: 都是些会频繁用到的基础材料。
barkText.en: Just a stash of basic materials people commonly use.

barkText.cn: 总算有时间补充炸弹了。
barkText.en: Finally, time to restock on bombs.

barkText.cn: 晚辈武陵城黎风，失礼了！
barkText.en: Lifeng of Wuling, ready to fight!
A definitive outcome.

barkText.cn: 谢谢，但我应该能做得更好。
barkText.en: Thank you, but I could've done better.

barkText.cn: 那边那个……就算再累也有跑一趟的价值。
barkText.en: Look there... Could be worth the trouble.

barkText.cn: 咦？这里我们是不是没来过？
barkText.en: Wait. We've never been here before, right?
...I miscalculated.

barkText.cn: 作战服有反应欸，那边有什么异常状况吗？
barkText.en: My combat outfit is reacting to something. Is there an anomaly over there?

barkText.cn: 我们一起铸就了这场胜利。
barkText.en: Together we made this victory happen.
Grab my meds! Heal yourself!
Bring it on! You're fighting me!
Don't panic. Try this.

barkText.cn: 我在这躺会儿，没事的话不要吵醒我。
barkText.en: I'm gonna lie down for a bit. Don't wake me unless something really big happens.
How did you find that?
Wow! That looks like a great find!
Time to keep my eye peeled.

barkText.cn: 这附近有古怪，您千万留意！
barkText.en: This place doesn't feel right. Be careful.
Just part of my job.
I know.

barkText.cn: 收集到了不少实用性较强的物资，是好事。
barkText.en: Great. We've gathered plenty of useful supplies.
It's all thanks to our solid teamwork.
Everyone has earned their share of glory.

barkText.cn: 把握每个补充资源的机会，才不会在关键时刻功亏一篑。
barkText.en: Always resupply when you can. You don't want to run short at critical moments.
That was ... a little too close. Quick. Tend to the wounded!

barkText.cn: 我查到记录说管理员参与过好几次重要的战役，有些传闻也是那时候留下的。
barkText.en: But I found records of important battles fought by our Endmin. They gave rise to quite a few stories.

barkText.cn: 我们需要帮助管理员尽快恢复状态。
barkText.en: In any case, we should expedite the restoration of our Endmin's health and memories.
I ... I did not.
Let's do our best, people!
Wow! Amazing!
This is great.
Uh, congrats!

barkText.cn: 固执的迷途者就在附近徘徊。我的术杖会为其哀哭。
barkText.en: A wayward, fallen one roams nearby. My staff shall grieve for them.
Yeah! Freeze them!

barkText.cn: 是强敌……我可以只负责支援吗？
barkText.en: High threat hostile... Mind if I stick to support?

barkText.cn: 老练的猎人知道怎么从风中获取讯息，无论是未来的气候还是猎物的行踪……
barkText.en: An experienced hunter can read the winds, and use it to predict the weather ... or to track the prey...
Everyone's chipping in!
Incredible move!
Good!
Impressive!
You did well.

barkText.cn: 希望之后也能这么顺利。
barkText.en: Hope every battle turns out this easy.

barkText.cn: 我们就这样继续吧，一鼓作气！
barkText.en: Let's keep going and finish this!
Heheh. You're too kind.
C'mon, spare me the theatrics.
Nice words, but save yourself some breath.

barkText.cn: 毕竟咱们是精英团队嘛。
barkText.en: Well, we are an elite team, after all.

barkText.cn: 结局总归是好的，别计较那么多。
barkText.en: That was close! Still gotta say — a win's a win.

barkText.cn: 眼前的敌人非同小可，提高警惕。
barkText.en: Stay alert. This hostile poses significant threat.
Feeling great today, eh?
A good gang makes it easy.

barkText.cn: 我见过其他人使用宏山的剑法，但即便是同样的剑招，每个人的章法也不尽相同……
barkText.en: You know, I've seen other Hongshan swordmancers, and everyone seems to perform the same move differently...
Hoo... I'm feeling better!
...I slipped.
Don't get hit by this!

barkText.cn: 暖融融的感觉，真喜欢。一路上脏兮兮、湿哒哒的，找到一个温暖干净的地方，真不容易。
barkText.en: Aww, this warm and cozy vibe is just perfect. After being all messy and wet, finding a clean and toasty spot like this is a little slice of heaven.
Ahh... I think I saw this before...

barkText.cn: 那里的敌人好像很危险，要小心哦。
barkText.en: Be extra careful! That enemy looks really dangerous.

barkText.cn: 让我们把这些矿物放进背包里！
barkText.en: Let's pack up these minerals!

barkText.cn: 哇，里面的东西好好看啊。
barkText.en: Wow, that's some nice-looking bling.
I'm good! I can still do this!
Nice moves.
Great teamwork.

barkText.cn: 最好的永远是下一场战斗，大家稳住。
barkText.en: Victory loves preparation. Keep pushing, team.

barkText.cn: 要收集这个吗？了解，我会继续留意。
barkText.en: Are we collecting this? Understood, I'll keep an eye out.
Arts Unit optimal.
Hurrr... The weapon's so heavy...

barkText.cn: 侵蚀的危害比常人以为的更可怕，必须慎重对待。
barkText.en: Blight is more dangerous than what is commonly believed. We must deal with it carefully.
Our teamwork just keeps getting better.
You flatter me.
You have keen senses.
Sharp eyes.

barkText.cn: 课本上讲过这些东西！是不是很值钱啊？
barkText.en: I've seen these in textbooks! Are they valuable?

barkText.cn: 那当然，也不看看我是谁！
barkText.en: Uh-huh. Greatness is kinda my thing!
Beautiful teamwork.

barkText.cn: 这个嘛，宏山的剑术在意不在形，领会剑意比拘泥具体的一招一式更重要。
barkText.en: Well, Hongshan swordmancy focuses on the will, not the form. Being one with the blade is far more important...

barkText.cn: 非凡的战利品，这足以宣告狩猎的丰收。
barkText.en: Outstanding loot. This hunt has proved itself fruitful.
Brace for impact!
Woohoho, this is way more than I imagined!
Guess I have to give you more credit now.
That's terrific!
To serenity they shall return.
I pray that the land accepts you all.

barkText.cn: 那附近我们还没去过，最好留意下。
barkText.en: We haven't been over there yet. Better make a note.
Wow... Very nice.
Hmm. Great...
Not too bad at all...

barkText.cn: 离成为主力又近了一步！
barkText.en: We're getting there — slowly but surely.

barkText.cn: 接下来要复盘、总结……不过先欢呼胜利吧！
barkText.en: Next up is AAR, PCA ... but let's cheer for our victory first!

barkText.cn: 嗯，这么痛快的胜利一定要庆祝一下。
barkText.en: Hmph. This triumph deserves a real partay!
You responded like lightning!
Like wind and thunder we gave them a storm.
I see it too!
Roger that. Heading right over.

barkText.cn: 可恶！我要给速冻仔的功率提升五十倍，下次要赢我可就没那么容易了。
barkText.en: Blasted blightery! I'm upping Frost-e-Bytee's output by 5000 percent! Let's see how they beat that!

barkText.cn: 哼……遗憾，这位还是差了一点点。
barkText.en: Hmph. Not bad, but not quite enough.
Hmph, we taught them a lesson!

barkText.cn: 谢谢大家的配合！辛苦啦！
barkText.en: Great teamwork, everyone!
This feels familiar.

barkText.cn: 你可以再浪费一会儿时间，反正有我在。
barkText.en: Don't worry. I'm around. Just go ahead and waste your time some more.

barkText.cn: 我只选择效率最高的方式。
barkText.en: I prefer being clean and ammo efficient.
Let me do it. I'm strong.

barkText.cn: 试试这个……或许能帮到你……
barkText.en: Try this... Maybe it can help...

barkText.cn: 这批木材采集后可以直接投入生产。
barkText.en: This wood is ready to go straight into production.

barkText.cn: 矿物用途多样，可以多采集一些。
barkText.en: Minerals serve multiple purposes. We should gather some.
Watch it! Don't get hurt!
I'll leave that side to you.

barkText.cn: 所以或多或少会有点刻板印象，不过现在眼见为实了。
barkText.en: That probably gave them some ... incomplete views about you. But now you're here, we can finally set things right.

barkText.cn: 在你苏醒之前，他们对你的了解主要来自有限的历史资料，还有捕风捉影的传闻。
barkText.en: Before you awoke, all they had were scraps of records and scattered rumors to learn about you.

barkText.cn: 休整完毕，继续推进作战任务。
barkText.en: Rest is complete. Let's proceed with the mission.
Your eyes are sharp.
It's there! Let's head over already!
Got my eyes peeled for an opening.
We handled that fight well!

barkText.cn: 这下送信的道路将会畅通无阻！
barkText.en: We just opened up the way for future deliveries!
Oh, i-it's over there?
I saw it too! Uh ... I think I did...
Tsk... This won't kill me.
Lucky we have you here!
I almost missed this one!

barkText.cn: 破坏成功！记得检查一下防侵蚀涂层的受损程度哦！
barkText.en: Elimination success! And check for any damages on your Blight-resistant coating, people!

barkText.cn: 小心，附近有难缠的家伙。
barkText.en: Watch it! That one can rough you up real bad.
Elite hostile unit detected.

barkText.cn: 战斗开始，请以自身安全为优先。
barkText.en: Engaging. Stay safe, team.

barkText.cn: 小暴鸰，好好警戒，不要偷懒哦！
barkText.en: Tweety-Bomb! Stay frosty, and *NO* slacking.
You ... flatter me.
Well, everyone helped.

barkText.cn: 那边好像有些资源，别忘了去收回呀。
barkText.en: Those resources seem useful. Don't forget to pick them up.

barkText.cn: 希望之后也能这么顺利。
barkText.en: Hope every battle turns out this easy.

barkText.cn: 人们是怎么看待塔卫二的？
barkText.en: So, what do people think about Talos-II?

barkText.cn: 那个看起来还不错……嗯，找个机会带回去吧。
barkText.en: That one looks good... If possible, we should bring it back.
Fire support, hot and ready!
Hope it's useful.

barkText.cn: 注意提防，那边的敌手不容小觑。
barkText.en: Stay alert, the enemy there is strong.

barkText.cn: 师者会对这些东西感兴趣的。
barkText.en: My Aldertone will be interested in these.

barkText.cn: 小心！那个敌人看起来好厉害！
barkText.en: Careful! That enemy looks really powerful!

barkText.cn: 请允许我去探究其中的奥秘。
barkText.en: Allow me to investigate this mystery.

barkText.cn: 走路留心脚边的好东西！
barkText.en: Watch your step, there could be goodies around!

barkText.cn: 哇！都是我们需要的东西！
barkText.en: Wow! This is exactly what we need!
Try this. It should help!
This makes me feel like I'm at home.

barkText.cn: 没错，我就是这么厉害哦。
barkText.en: Yep, that's just how awesome I am.

barkText.cn: 醚质，也是塔卫二的语言。
barkText.en: Aurylene ... another language whispered by Talos-II.

barkText.cn: 这附近竟然还有连我都没去过的地方？
barkText.en: Oh, I can't believe there are places I've never visited before!
We achieved an ideal outcome.

barkText.cn: 都解决了吗？再检查一下吧。
barkText.en: Area neutralized? Better run another check.

barkText.cn: 应该给武器加装一个采矿专用模块的。
barkText.en: Should've furnished my pewpews with a specialized mining module.
You've got eyes like a hawk.
Wooo, good stuff again?

barkText.cn: 呀，这就结束了？我还有几招没使……
barkText.en: Is that it? I haven't even shown you my best moves...
Now that's what I call a real fight!

barkText.cn: 指针在跳动，附近也许有好东西。
barkText.en: My device is ticking. Maybe there's something nice nearby.
We did it as a team.
This is the power of Endfield.

barkText.cn: 又一处未被人类探索的区域。
barkText.en: Another area uncharted by humanity.

barkText.cn: 侵蚀会干扰行动计划，正确的判断。
barkText.en: You made the right call. The Blight only impedes our operation.
Incoming! Unknown hazard!
Preparing tactical support.

barkText.cn: 太好了，这下不会有人受伤了。
barkText.en: Great. Now it'll no longer hurt anyone.

barkText.cn: 没关系，就像信使家族流传下来的一条箴言：要走好路，不要看着脚下，要看着远方。
barkText.en: There's an old saying among the Messengers: To walk the right path, don't focus on where you step — keep your eyes on the horizon.
Impressive!
You did well.
Good!
That was just bad luck. One more round.

barkText.cn: 对不起！肯定是我哪里犯错了！我会反省的。所、所以，再试一次吧？
barkText.en: I'm so sorry! It-it-it's all my fault! I'll ... I'll fix what went wrong. How about ... we try again?

barkText.cn: 这样开采是不是有点伤武器？
barkText.en: Won't manual mining chip our weapons?

barkText.cn: 每一次的休整都尤为重要。这意味着在下一场战斗来临前，你还有准备的机会。
barkText.en: Every chance of recuperation counts. It might be your only chance to prepare for the next battle.
I just happen to need some practice.
Phew. I thought I was done for.
That's admirable.
Outstanding.
Commendable.
Th-that's ... so cool...
Everyone's so incredible!
Good... At least it ended quickly...

barkText.cn: 需、需要冷饮吗？我可以帮忙冰镇一点……
barkText.en: A-an-anyone want something cold to drink? I can make them cold for you...

barkText.cn: 那边有你不该遗忘的东西。
barkText.en: Something worth remembering there.

barkText.cn: 这在荒野上不常见，值得好好利用。
barkText.en: A rarity in the wildlands. We'll make good use of it.
Keen sights.
Not bad. I didn't even notice that.

barkText.cn: 受难之人今天并非你我。
barkText.en: He who suffers today is not among us.
Watch out! Get back!
Remarkable performance.
You did very well.
Excellent.
I find joy in the language of celebration.

barkText.cn: 武陵的孩子从小就跟侵蚀打交道，小事儿，交给我！
barkText.en: The Blight's nothing new to us Wuling kids. Don't worry, I got this one!
Impressive... Only you could pull that off.
Bravo!
Nice, high five!
Yeah, kudos to you!
Intel received!
You really got a sharp eye!

barkText.cn: 这是否意味着，我们对侵蚀有了更深的了解……
barkText.en: Does this mean we have achieved better understanding of the Blight...?
Phooo... Feeling better already.
These minerals may come in handy.
Hostile attack order detected.
Good deeds be praised.
Everyone okay?
My body ... is feeling so heavy...

barkText.cn: 偷偷告诉你，那儿都是好东西！
barkText.en: Psst. Got a secret for you. The stuff over there is made of awesome!
Victory goes without saying.
This hardly counts as warm-up.
Everyone is rested.
Blight elimination confirmed.

barkText.cn: 速度会慢些，但还能继续。
barkText.en: Still in the fight, just a bit slower.
That was an oversight.

barkText.cn: 猎手与猎物本就是一念之差……重整旗鼓吧。
barkText.en: The hunter can sometimes become the hunted... I say it's time to begin the chase anew.

barkText.cn: 比起完胜，有缺憾的胜利更有参考意义。
barkText.en: A flawless win teaches little. It's the flaws that sharpen us.
That's some perfect observation.
You made the right call.

barkText.cn: 嗯，它们在很多地方都能派上用场。
barkText.en: Good. We'll have many uses for this finding.
It's all about our teamwork!

barkText.cn: 多亏了大家的助攻！光荣属于我们！
barkText.en: Couldn't have done it without you all!

barkText.cn: 那边有值得注意的东西。
barkText.en: Something calls for our attention over there.
A textbook maneuver.
A brilliant strategy.

barkText.cn: 配合得不错！你的铳法还是那么精准。
barkText.en: Good work. You are a true sharpshooter.
All set. Back to the fight.

barkText.cn: 伸伸懒腰，揉揉腿——够不着啊……呼，舒坦！
barkText.en: Need a leg rub — Hngh... Can't reach... Hooo. Much better!

barkText.cn: 这里不会再受到侵蚀的阻隔了。
barkText.en: This will get the Blight out of the way.

barkText.cn: 哇……从、从来没见过这么多好东西……
barkText.en: Woooooww... I've never seen nice things like these...
Heheh, caught it before it flew away.

barkText.cn: 似乎有值得调查的东西……
barkText.en: Something seems to warrant closer scrutiny...

barkText.cn: 在我们的路途上，这只是一个可变向量。
barkText.en: This amorphous material is just a variable on our trek.
Evade! I'll cover you!

barkText.cn: 战斗中总有不可控的变量，这是我们能取得的最好成果。
barkText.en: Our results are optimal, despite the unexpected variables of combat.
Cool.
Amazing. Want me to clap?
Nice.

barkText.cn: 这就是手册上说过的“醚质”吧……
barkText.en: This must be the Aurylene mentioned in the manual...
We appreciate your hard work!

barkText.cn: 踏出开始那一步总是最难的。
barkText.en: The first step is always the hardest.

barkText.cn: 现在，这些污秽挡不住我们了。
barkText.en: Now these filthy obstacles no longer hinder our advance.

barkText.cn: 比传闻中更加难以捉摸。
barkText.en: I would say that you're more mysterious than what the stories claim.

barkText.cn: 把一封信送到终点的旅途，或许会坎坷不平，但没关系，我们会再次启程。
barkText.en: The road might be fraught with hardship, but we will start our journey again, and ensure a successful delivery.

barkText.cn: 那边有些东西，没用的话，就拿来试剑吧。
barkText.en: See something there. If it's useless, we can use it to test our blades.
You're welcome!
We're doing good, team!
Phew... I feel so much better.

barkText.cn: 确认高危险目标，别慌，我们演习过应对策略。
barkText.en: High-risk target detected. Stay calm, we've trained for this.
I'll hold to the end.
Hang in there. No rush.

barkText.cn: 让我们轻松地解决战斗！
barkText.en: We'll end this fight easily!
This will boost our efficiency.

barkText.cn: 嗯……今天也听到了很多美妙的声音……
barkText.en: Hmm... Another day of beautiful sounds...
Wow! You can actually do that?!

barkText.cn: 太精彩了！我们可以再来一次吗？
barkText.en: Awesome! Can we do it again?
I'm with you.
I'll keep this Aurylene for you.
I'm in the flow.

barkText.cn: 那、那边有好东西……对吧？我没看错吧？
barkText.en: That looks like something nice... If I'm not seeing things...

barkText.cn: 好漂亮……啊，没什么！收集工作完成了！
barkText.en: It's so beautiful... Oh, sorry! I'm done gathering it!

barkText.cn: 嗯，那边的东西……就算需要绕路，也是值得的。
barkText.en: There's something over there... It's worth looking into, even if we need to take a detour.
That's commendable.
Outstanding.
Nice job.
Hey! Get out the way!

barkText.cn: 没想到吧，战斗对我来说也不在话下。
barkText.en: FYI, I'm also quite the combat expert.

barkText.cn: 赢啦！我要拍张照纪念一下。
barkText.en: Victory is ours! Time for a selfie.

barkText.cn: 作为救援物资储备起来吧！
barkText.en: Let's add this to our emergency stockpile!
We should let Nature take its course.

barkText.cn: 多希望这种场合能用上自动矿机……
barkText.en: If only someone brought an auto-mining rig...

barkText.cn: 喔哦……刚才的动作我可不行。
barkText.en: Wow... I would never pull that off.

barkText.cn: 没错……就应该多依靠团队协作。
barkText.en: Good... Team work is what we need.
That's a very detailed observation.
Thanks for the reminder.
A very timely reminder.
We almost missed that.
I'm still in fighting shape...
They show lethal intent!

barkText.cn: 多亏了……大家……还好坚持下来了……
barkText.en: Everyone ... did well... I'm so glad I made it...

barkText.cn: 自己动手，这算忆苦思甜么？
barkText.en: Ah, the good ol' DIY. Just like the bitter old days.

barkText.cn: 管理员，看到了吗？刚才那招怎么样？
barkText.en: How's that, Endmin? Did you see that move I did?
Such is the will of Nature.
Steady your breathing.

barkText.cn: 失败并不可怕，只要从中吸取经验教训，下次一定会做得更好。
barkText.en: Losing isn't the end of the world. Learn from the experience and we'll do better next time.

barkText.cn: 各位……成功与失败并不是0和1的运算符，它们会组成无数种复杂的诗。
barkText.en: My friends ... success and failure are not binary like 0 and 1. A spectrum of countless nuances lies between them.

barkText.cn: 附近有需要调查的区域。
barkText.en: The nearby area needs a proper survey.
Hmm. Not bad at all.
Good stuff.
Very impressive.

barkText.cn: 放心去看看吧，跟在我身后就行了。
barkText.en: We can go take a look. No worries. Just stay close behind me.

barkText.cn: 这片侵蚀搞定了！呼，累死我了。
barkText.en: Blight neutralized! Hurrr. This is so exhausting.
Exemplary combat maneuver.
Outstanding performance.
Look, over there...

barkText.cn: 跟我来，上次路过这儿，我做过宝藏的标记！
barkText.en: Follow me! I left a treasure mark here last time I was around!

barkText.cn: 很好，管理员，一切都在你的计划之中。
barkText.en: Excellent work, Endmin. Everything worked according to your plans.

barkText.cn: 呼……得去那边探索一番了。
barkText.en: Hooo... I guess we'll have to investigate that area.

barkText.cn: 周旋并不只是靠说话，前提是——手腕够硬。
barkText.en: Talk's cheap, mate. Gotta put in the hard yakka.

barkText.cn: 不客气，我们是以此为生的。
barkText.en: No worries, it's all part of our job.

barkText.cn: 我一个人也……不，麻烦各位了。
barkText.en: Maybe just let me handle... Actually, let's finish this as a team.
Where should we go next?
Cool. Glad we're on the same page.
Yup, I see it too.
You did good!
You got keen eyes!
Fine vision you have. Yes, it's right there!
Keen is your sight.

barkText.cn: 休息好了，鼓足干劲上吧。
barkText.en: I had a great nap. Time for some serious action.

barkText.cn: 大家一起来？肯定很快就能采完啦！
barkText.en: Let's do this together. It'll make things faster.

barkText.cn: 刚才浮游炮攻击轨迹有些许偏离，是哪里出问题了吗？
barkText.en: Orbiter attack trajectory offset detected. I may need to initiate troubleshooting.

barkText.cn: 不错，出招比之前更快了。
barkText.en: Impressive. You got faster.

barkText.cn: 高质量的矿物，也许能用在临时庇护所的搭建上……
barkText.en: High quality minerals. We can probably use them for building temporary shelters...
I shall fulfill my role of support.
Incoming! Watch out!
Returning is my strength.
Stay calm, let's get you patched up first.

barkText.cn: 打得酣畅淋漓——就是，嘿，肚子饿了。
barkText.en: THAT was a good battle — Ah, well, it's time for food.
That's why you're the boss!
We're in perfect sync.
You pulled off a sleek move.
Blight elimination confirmed.
High-threat hostile. Approach with caution.
Don't stop. Keep moving.

barkText.cn: 我们会把这些光球捉进瓶子里照明。
barkText.en: We usually bottle them to give light.
A gift of the Law.

barkText.cn: 请指引我们的前路，向我们揭示永远的宁静吧。
barkText.en: Kindly guide us to the revealing of eternal tranquility.

barkText.cn: 前方有危险的敌人，我们一定要做好万全准备。
barkText.en: Something dangerous is up ahead. We better be fully prepared.

barkText.cn: 发现高价值目标，请求优先回收。
barkText.en: High-value object identified. Requesting approval for retrieval.

barkText.cn: 特别的战利品，我们应该拿下它们。
barkText.en: Special loot in sight. We should grab it.

barkText.cn: 难怪开拓区外围的定居点时常传来遭裂地者袭扰的报告，却又总是追踪不到他们……
barkText.en: That explains why the settlements on the frontier outskirts kept reporting Landbreaker attacks, but we were never able to track them down…
E-everyone made it happen!
Y-you flatter me!
Emergency treatment administered!
I'm still in fighting shape...

barkText.cn: 棘手的味道，我们的对手并不简单。
barkText.en: Smells like trouble. This is no ordinary enemy.

barkText.cn: 呼……我不是在逃避问题，我只是需要休息一下……好了，让我们重启吧。
barkText.en: Phooo... I am definitely not ignoring the errors. I am simply in need of rest. Well then, let us reboot this process once more.

barkText.cn: 危险程度未知，建议慎重行动。
barkText.en: Threat level unavailable. We should be cautious.

barkText.cn: 趁我还有体力，找找看吧……
barkText.en: Let's keep looking while I still have my strength...

barkText.cn: 有什么发现吗？……慢慢找吧。
barkText.en: Found anything...? Let's just ... take our time.
Fine quality ore!

barkText.cn: 是十分珍贵的物资储备，足以影响战局。
barkText.en: Strategic reserves like these can shift the tide of battle.
A timely treatment!
Nicely done! Ever thought about taking up my job?

barkText.cn: 瞧瞧我们，像真正的一家人一样！
barkText.en: Look at us, pulling together like a real brood!
...We'll fight them again!
Now we've made good on this trip.
No trouble at all!
Good. A new discovery has been made.

barkText.cn: 看见那个家伙了？要我出手吗？
barkText.en: See that one? Need me to do some trimming?

barkText.cn: 别在意我，按你的步调来。
barkText.en: Don't mind me. I'll keep up with your tempo.

barkText.cn: 终于赢了……因为大家始终没有放弃，我们才没有失败。
barkText.en: We finally pulled it off... And it's because we all stuck together.
I'm with you.

barkText.cn: 下一次……下一次我会更加全力以赴的……不能就这么结束……
barkText.en: I can't let it end like this... Next time ... I'll try even harder...

barkText.cn: 大家……都没事吗……活着的感觉……真好啊……
barkText.en: Is everyone okay...? Oh ... feels good to be alive...
This is one rewarding trip.
Heheh. Yeah ... I'll go lighter on them next time.

barkText.cn: 那个那个！带回去研究研究。
barkText.en: Ohhhh! Gotta take that one back for my studies.
Wonderful!
You've set a great example for us!
That's incredible!

barkText.cn: 随便折腾吧，我会保护好你们。
barkText.en: Do it your way. I'll keep you covered.
Careful, don't get jinxed.
All units! Incoming!

barkText.cn: 大开眼界了！我也不能落后！
barkText.en: That was incredible! I'm fired up!
How'd you do that? Please teach me!

barkText.cn: 那些资源都很重要哦，让我们多收集一些吧。
barkText.en: These resources are really important. Let's try to gather more.
Thanks for the reminder.
That's a very detailed observation.

barkText.cn: 发呆……反正战术手册里没有要求，要来一些破冰游戏吗？
barkText.en: Since the tactics manual doesn't have any rules against fun, how about we play some icebreaker games? What do you think?
Take this. We still got plenty.
Everyone okay?

barkText.cn: 老师说，野外飘浮的醚质其实很安全，只是不要追得太深。
barkText.en: My mentor said the floating Aurylenes in the wilds aren't really dangerous. Just don't go after them recklessly.

barkText.cn: 嗯，会有很多人因此受益的。
barkText.en: Yes it will. Many will benefit from its removal.

barkText.cn: 附近似乎有高价值的物资，值得留意。
barkText.en: We seem to have high value supplies nearby. Keep an eye out for those.
The light of Veritas shines upon you.
My heart rejoices for you.
So wonderful...
Watch it! Don't get hit!
This is far from desperate.
Conditions sub-optimal, but still functional.
Nice! Looks like we've made quite the haul!
The trek grows ... more arduous...
Just doing what I must.
This isn't my best.
A blade unsheathed, its light unleashed!
I'm here to help. Heehee.
You flatter me.

barkText.cn: 你们证明了团队的价值。
barkText.en: We have proven the power of unity.
Good call.
Very observant.

barkText.cn: 得来不易的好东西，想清楚了再用吧。
barkText.en: Took a lot to get this. Let's put it to good use.

barkText.cn: 好，相信我们之间的默契！
barkText.en: Let's go! I have total faith in y'all!

barkText.cn: 难道你没看见那边的……啊，我什么都没说。
barkText.en: Did you see that over there? Oh, never mind, forget I said anything.

barkText.cn: 这里不会再受到侵蚀的阻隔了。
barkText.en: This will get the Blight out of the way.

barkText.cn: 各位，确认一下自己的状况吧。
barkText.en: Verify and report personal status, team.

barkText.cn: 出色的配合，必然的结果。
barkText.en: A definitive outcome achieved through strong teamwork.
We achieved tacit synergy.
An outstanding performance.

barkText.cn: 暴力并非我们的目的，继续前进吧。
barkText.en: Violence is never our objective. Let's press forward.
About time.

barkText.cn: 真可惜，对面本来有机会的。
barkText.en: Too bad, they almost had a chance.
Good, one less problem to worry about.

barkText.cn: 休整是为了更好地出发。
barkText.en: Proper rest prepares us for a longer journey.

barkText.cn: 不要心急，调整完毕后再做打算。
barkText.en: No need to worry. We'll regroup and figure this out.
Excellent.
A well-deserved finding.
Suits you well, it does!

barkText.cn: 每个人都是团队不可或缺的一部分。
barkText.en: Everyone has been indispensable to the team.

barkText.cn: 胜利总是代价高昂……珍视你由此得到的，勿忘你为此失去的。
barkText.en: Every victory bears its price... Hold dear what you've learned, but don't forget what we've paid.
*Yawn* Coming. Y'all are so productive.

barkText.cn: 运气不错，占卜节目没骗我。
barkText.en: Lucky. Turned out the tarot show is legit.
Gotta treat myself sometimes.
Let me help you!
We won't let this happen again...

barkText.cn: 好像找到了不得了的东西呢，或许能在以后的行动中发挥很大作用！
barkText.en: Seems like a terrific discovery. Perhaps they'll be useful for future operations!

barkText.cn: 要过去看看吗？万一是什么值钱的东西呢？
barkText.en: Probably should take a look. Maybe it's worth something.

barkText.cn: 如果有作战需求，我会提前规划好撤退方案。
barkText.en: If combat is required, I'll ready our exit plan in advance.

barkText.cn: 如果不想错过重要的物资，最好留心下那里。
barkText.en: Keep an eye on that area, if you don't want to miss key supplies.

barkText.cn: 那里似乎有个厉害的家伙，让我来试试手吧。
barkText.en: Danger up ahead. Lemme see how good this one is.
The decision is sound.
Good observation skills.

barkText.cn: 没啥抹不开面儿的，我来给大伙弄点好东西。吃饱了咱们再干回去！
barkText.en: No need to fret. I'll make food for the team and avenge this defeat!
Much better now.

barkText.cn: 计算的圣洁之处在于它的绝对中立——既能算出成功，也能算出失败，这再也正常不过。
barkText.en: The sacredness of computation lies in its perfect neutrality — The algorithms predict both success and failure. Keep faith and carry on.

barkText.cn: 抽刀断水大概也是这种感觉吧。
barkText.en: One can't stop a flood with a single blade. Perhaps this is what it felt like.
My prayers have been answered.

barkText.cn: 真知短暂地触摸过这里！
barkText.en: Veritas has graced this battlefield with its touch!

barkText.cn: 还好还好，差点连我这口大铁锅都给砸咯！
barkText.en: That was close. They almost broke my iron wok.
Hngh! I'm alright! Focus on the fight.
Hngh... It hurts... They got me bad...
The results speak for themselves.
Our battle plan proved its worth.

barkText.cn: 醚质……和记忆一样飘忽不定。
barkText.en: Aurylene... A thing that's just as unreliable as my memories.

barkText.cn: 这也是对您一路辛苦的慰劳！
barkText.en: A reward for the difficulties we faced!
Good work, everyone.
We made another step forward, Endfielders.

barkText.cn: 试错也能带来宝贵的经验，我们对胜利有了更大的把握，不是吗？
barkText.en: Mistakes help us learn. I'm sure we can do better next time.
They can't handle my lance!

barkText.cn: 那里有些能带走的东西。
barkText.en: There's something we can gather over there.
We'll see this through!
Evade!

barkText.cn: 醚质是行动时的高优先级目标，它究竟有什么秘密？
barkText.en: Acquiring Aurylene is our top priority on missions. I wonder what secret it hides...
Careful. There's something weird nearby.
Alright, Chen. That's enough flattery for the day...
"So wowed and amazed"...??

barkText.cn: 你总是盯着那个方向看，是有什么吗？
barkText.en: You're always staring in that direction. What's over there?

barkText.cn: 裂地者主要活跃在荒地上，游荡在文明环带的边界。
barkText.en: The Landbreakers usually keep to the wildlands along the fringes of civilization.

barkText.cn: 除了规模较大的氏族，大部分裂地者都会经常更换自己的驻地。这让他们的行踪难以捉摸。
barkText.en: Only the largest clans could lay claim to a permanent territory. Others are constantly on the move, making them quite difficult to track...

barkText.cn: 专心战斗，我会掩护你们。
barkText.en: Focus on the battle. I shall provide covering fire.
Careful. That one looks like serious trouble.
The gang made it happen.
Just doing my job.
I am here to manifest blessings.

barkText.cn: 不要轻易放弃！等大家重新做好准备，再尝试一次吧！
barkText.en: Don't give up! Let's suit up and do our prep work! Then we'll do this again!

barkText.cn: 好像有很值钱的东西，要发财了。
barkText.en: Looks valuable. Guess we're gonna be rich.
We won. That's what matters.

barkText.cn: 根据小队刚才的受损情况，撤退是我在计算后得出的最优解。
barkText.en: Tabulations of losses incurred showed that extraction was the best solution for the team.

barkText.cn: 那些物资，要去收集一下吗？
barkText.en: I see resources over there... Should we go and collect them?
